text: Frédéric Reiss (born November 12, 1949) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Bas-Rhin department, and is a member of the Republicans. He is the mayor of Niederbronn-les-Bains, Bas-Rhin. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:People from Haguenau Category:Mayors of places in Grand Est Category:Radical Party (France) politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:The Social Right Category:Modern and Humanist France Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:French people of German descent
